Package: srmta
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser, ca-certificates
Recommends: postgresql, redis-server
Description: Scalable RFC-Compliant Mail Transfer Agent
 SRMTA is a production-grade, horizontally scalable, RFC 5321/5322 compliant
 Mail Transfer Agent built in Go. Features include:
 .
  * ESMTP with STARTTLS, AUTH (PLAIN/LOGIN), and pipelining
  * Multi-spool queue: incoming/active/deferred/retry/dead-letter/failed
  * Crash recovery journal with write-ahead log
  * DKIM signing with multi-key support
  * Bounce classification and auto-suppression
  * IP pool health scoring with warm-up controls
  * DNS resolver with caching and MX fallback
  * Prometheus metrics exporter
  * config.d/ sub-config support for modular configuration
